RAINBOW

CSS Color Framework

Created by Rashidul Hasan

1343 Color Codes Based on Pantone Coated Colors. CSS Classes are Available for Background, Text, Border/Outline, SVG Fill & SVG Stroke Colors.

HOW TO USE
Copy the css link and paste it inside your page <head></head> tag: <link href="rainbow/rainbow.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
Then call css class in your design: <div class="bg-17 txt-1">Hello Rainbow :)</div>

RESULT

Hello Rainbow :)

2. RGBA
